Vampirtron:

     The scans were over. Vampirtron could barely stand, but he managed to pull a computer stand over to him to view the results. They were what he expected.

     His body contained no Spark, he needed the &quot;blood&quot; of Transformers to survive. But something interesting was also of note, he could manage to survive and not drink the blood of transformers. The Vampiric side of him didn&#39;t want to share this information. But the good side of him knew he had to.

     &quot;Kenzo, I need to run an experiment soon,&quot; He said, sitting straight up, &quot;But I need to contact Rodimus. He needs to be here for this.&quot;

     He stumbled over to the comm system and hit the buttons for Rodimus, &quot;Rodimus, it&#39;s Vampirtron, I hate to interrupt you, but I think I&#39;ve found a solution to my problem, and I want you here to see for yourself.&quot;

     After that was said he collapsed on the floor, passed out.

